---
title: Ginger Shrimp Stir-Fry with Hoisin Bacon
description: Freshly ground ginger packs the punch for tonight's Asian-inspired shrimp stir-fry! Oh, and did we mention it's also topped with hoisin bacon... ya, we did that!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/saute-de-crevettes-au-gingembre-ce0fc975.jpg
